◆ AEM13920_BSTCFG_t

struct AEM13920_BSTCFG_t

Bost converter configuration.

Data Fields
bool enable:1 Enable/Disable the boost converter.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool high_power_enable:1 Enable/Disable the High Power feature for the boost converter.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

AEM13920_TMULT tmult:3 Boost converter's timing multiplier.

Set the timing multiplier for the boost converter. The higher the timing multiplier, the higher the average current pulled from the source to charge the storage element

uint8_t __rsvd:3 Reserved.

◆ AEM13920_IRQEN_t

struct AEM13920_IRQEN_t

IRQ settings.

Data Fields
bool i2c_rdy:1 Enable/Disable the generation of interrupts when the AEM is out of reset and ready to communicate.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool vovdis:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the storage level crosses the overdischarge threshold.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool vchrdy:1 Enable/Disablethe IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the storage level crosses the charge ready threshold.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool vovch:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the storage level crosses the overcharge threshold.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool src_low:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) on any transition between a state where at least one source voltage is above its low threshold and a state where both are below their respective thresholds.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool temp_ch:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the ambient temperature is out of the defined range for storage element charging.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool temp_dis:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the ambient temperature is out of the defined range for storage element discharging.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

uint8_t __rsvd:1 reserved
bool src1_mppt_start:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the MPPT starts for SRC1.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool src1_mppt_done:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the MPPT is done for SRC1.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool src2_mppt_start:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the MPPT starts for SRC2.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool src2_mppt_done:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when the MPPT is done for SRC2.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool sto_done:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) wwhen a new data from the STO ADC is available.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool temp_done:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when a new data from the temperature ADC is available.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool apm_done:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when new APM data are available.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

bool apm_err:1 Enable/Disable the IRQ pin to be asserted (HIGH) when an APM error occurs.

Set to true to enable, to false to disable

◆ AEM13920_STATUS_t

struct AEM13920_STATUS_t

Status.

Data Fields
bool vovdis:1 Overdischarge status.

Set to true when the storage level is under the overdischarge threshold, to false otherwise

bool vchrdy:1 Charge ready status.

Set to true when the storage level is above the charge ready threshold, to false otherwise

bool vovch:1 Overcharge status.

Set to true when the storage level is above the overcharge threshold, to false otherwise

bool src1_low:1 SRC1LOW threshold status.

Set to true when the SRC1's voltage is under the defined threshold, to false otherwise

bool src2_low:1 SRC2LOW threshold status.

Set to true when the SRC2 voltage is under the defined threshold, to false otherwise

uint8_t __rsvd0:3 Reserved.
bool temp_cold_ch:1 Cold temperature threshold for storage element charging status.

Set to true when the temperature is below the cold threshold, to false otherwise

bool temp_hot_ch:1 Hot temperature threshold for storage element charging status.

Set to true when the temperature is above the hot threshold, to false otherwise

bool temp_cold_dis:1 Cold Temperature threshold for storage element discharging status.

Set to true when the temperature is below the cold threshold, to false otherwise

bool temp_hot_dis:1 Hot temperature threshold for storage element discharging status.

Set to true when the temperature is above the hot threshold, to false otherwise

uint8_t __rsvd1:4 Reserved.

◆ AEM13920_APMERR_t

struct AEM13920_APMERR_t

APM Error.

Data Fields
bool src1_ov:1 SRC1 counter overflow.

Set to true when a counter overflow has occured, to false otherwise

bool src1_nvld:1 SRC1 counter corrupted.

Set to true when the counter is corrupted, to false otherwise

bool src2_ov:1 SRC2 counter overflow.

Set to true when a counter overflow has occured, to false otherwise

bool src2_nvld:1 SRC2 counter corrupted.

Set to true when the counter is corrupted, to false otherwise

bool buck_ov:1 BUCK counter overflow.

Set to true when a counter overflow has occured, to false otherwise

bool buck_nvld:1 Buck counter corrupted.

Set to true when the counter is corrupted, to false otherwise

uint8_t __rsvd:2 reserved
